{"tid":932983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國人權專員稱欲訪新疆但被中國拒絕","createTime":"2018-12-08T07:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T16:00:25.000Z","uid":141151,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d116ba8688894d78740b0d36d550c76045a94f0d","tid":932983,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T07:47:31.000Z","msg":"德國人權專員稱欲訪新疆但被中國拒絕 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20181206/s00004/1544082779972/%e5%be%b7%e5%9c%8b%e4%ba%ba%e6%ac%8a%e5%b0%88%e5%93%a1%e7%a8%b1%e6%ac%b2%e8%a8%aa%e6%96%b0%e7%96%86%e4%bd%86%e8%a2%ab%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e6%8b%92%e7%b5%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20181206%2Fs00004%2F1544082779972%2F%25e5%25be%25b7%25e5%259c%258b%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%25ac%258a%25e5%25b0%2588%25e5%2593%25a1%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e6%25ac%25b2%25e8%25a8%25aa%25e6%2596%25b0%25e7%2596%2586%25e4%25bd%2586%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%258b%2592%25e7%25b5%2595&d=l8LDnSP6m40B1n5xzDpXwZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=bab23a5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20181206%2Fs00004%2F1544082779972%2F%25e5%25be%25b7%25e5%259c%258b%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%25ac%258a%25e5%25b0%2588%25e5%2593%25a1%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e6%25ac%25b2%25e8%25a8%25aa%25e6%2596%25b0%25e7%2596%2586%25e4%25bd%2586%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%258b%2592%25e7%25b5%2595&h=c0fb948b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20181206/s00004/1544082779972/%e5%be%b7%e5%9c%8b%e4%ba%ba%e6%ac%8a%e5%b0%88%e5%93%a1%e7%a8%b1%e6%ac%b2%e8%a8%aa%e6%96%b0%e7%96%86%e4%bd%86%e8%a2%ab%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e6%8b%92%e7%b5%95</a><br />\n<br />\n新疆人權問題引起國際關注，然而德國外交部周二（4日）引述該國人權政策及人道援助專員柯夫勒（Barbel Kofler）的一份聲明，指中國政府拒絕他進入新疆的請求。<br />\n<br />\n德國外交部指，柯夫勒周二起抵華訪問，並在今明兩日前往西藏拉薩，參與一年一度的中德人權對話。柯夫勒在聲明中表示，關注中國人權狀況，尤其對新疆維族人的「再教育營」感震驚，故希望在這次訪華期間，前往新疆取得第一手資料，但遭中國政府拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n另外，聯合國人權事務高級專員巴舍萊（Michelle Bachelet）周三（5日）表示，她閱覽聯合國收到的有關新疆人權狀況報告後，對當地情況感憂慮，計劃親自前往新疆查證，並希望中國政府可再次在這問題上與聯合國認真對話。不過，暫時未知有關行程是否成行。<br />\n<br />\n（美國有線新聞網絡）"},{"pid":"91dc4f993730c15f7f84876de605837622fded84","tid":932983,"uid":20170,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T07:50:01.000Z","msg":"又話歡迎大家到中國看看<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c566b96cfb850b693e3ac0ddb65571cf1e720e6b","tid":932983,"uid":50457,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T07:51:16.000Z","msg":"德國睇唔到的，香港警察看到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63892822ea4c17129841148a3285720029f8ec8","tid":932983,"uid":5063,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T08:00:44.000Z","msg":"睇返二戰集中營d片咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d99e2e4fac91fdaca2c9116525a90975f852cb8","tid":932983,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71433366d172241e144938cd9b0922156b6834ab","tid":932983,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T00:04:50.000Z","msg":"係時候到德國搞新疆旅行法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19702f2b0adf4b1673b8144253e906fbe51f726f","tid":932983,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T00:11:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b13760276afe0ae8d8738d1a000c0ef2d64fd2","tid":932983,"uid":56561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T00:26:41.000Z","msg":"就係唔同德國人分享治蛔方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/no